🚴‍♀️🧘‍♂️ Spin & Flow – The Ultimate Power Hour! 🔥✨

Get ready for the perfect fitness combo that brings the best of both worlds! Vanessa’s brand new Spin + Yoga class kicks off with 30 minutes of high-energy cycling to get your heart pumping, followed by 30 minutes of yoga flow to stretch it all out and find your calm.

It’s sweat, strength, and serenity—all in one power-packed hour.
Come for the burn, stay for the bliss!

📅 Now on the schedule – let’s ride, stretch, and glow!
